      "{\n",
      " \"cells\": [\n",
      "  {\n",
      "   \"cell_type\": \"markdown\",\n",
      "   \"id\": \"5b19fe31\",\n",
      "   \"metadata\": {},\n",
      "   \"source\": [\n",
      "    \"Exceptions are runtime errors that occur while a Python program is executing. Instead of terminating the program immediately, Python creates an exception object. If the exception is not handled, the program stops and displays an error message (called a traceback).\"\n",
      "   ]\n",
      "  },\n",
      "  {\n",
      "   \"cell_type\": \"code\",\n",
      "   \"execution_count\": null,\n",
      "   \"id\": \"f3f3a294\",\n",
      "   \"metadata\": {},\n",
      "   \"outputs\": [],\n",
      "   \"source\": [\n",
      "    \"# Without Exception Handling\\n\",\n",
      "    \"\\n\",\n",
      "    \"num = 10\\n\",\n",
      "    \"print(num / 0)\\n\",\n",
      "    \"\\n\",\n",
      "    \"print(\\\"Program End\\\")\"\n",
      "   ]\n",
      "  },\n",
      "  {\n",
      "   \"cell_type\": \"code\",\n",
      "   \"execution_count\": null,\n",
      "   \"id\": \"a1137716\",\n",
      "   \"metadata\": {},\n",
      "   \"outputs\": [],\n",
      "   \"source\": [\n",
      "    \"# With Exception Handling\\n\",\n",
      "    \"try:\\n\",\n",
      "    \"    num = 10\\n\",\n",
      "    \"    print(num / 0)\\n\",\n",
      "    \"except ZeroDivisionError:\\n\",\n",
      "    \"    print(\\\"Cannot divide by zero.\\\")\\n\",\n",
      "    \"\\n\",\n",
      "    \"print(\\\"Program End\\\")\"\n",
      "   ]\n",
      "  },\n",
      "  {\n",
      "   \"cell_type\": \"markdown\",\n",
      "   \"id\": \"1e187ca9\",\n",
      "   \"metadata\": {},\n",
      "   \"source\": [\n",
      "    \"### Exception Handling\\n\",\n",
      "    \"\\n\",\n",
      "    \"| **Keyword** | **Purpose**                                                   |\\n\",\n",
      "    \"| ----------- | ------------------------------------------------------------- |\\n\",\n",
      "    \"| `try`       | Wrap the block of code that might cause an exception.         |\\n\",\n",
      "    \"| `except`    | Handle the exception if it occurs.                            |\\n\",\n",
      "    \"| `else`      | Run code only if no exception occurs.                         |\\n\",\n",
      "    \"| `finally`   | Run code no matter what, whether there's an exception or not. |\\n\",\n",
      "    \"| `raise`     | Manually throw an exception.                                  |\\n\"\n",
      "   ]\n",
      "  },\n",
      "  {\n",
      "   \"cell_type\": \"markdown\",\n",
      "   \"id\": \"dc9ae926\",\n",
      "   \"metadata\": {},\n",
      "   \"source\": [\n",
      "    \"try:\\n\",\n",
      "    \"    # Code that may cause an exception\\n\",\n",
      "    \"except:\\n\",\n",
      "    \"    # Code to handle the exception\"\n",
      "   ]\n",
      "  },\n",
      "  {\n",
      "   \"cell_type\": \"code\",\n",
      "   \"execution_count\": 2,\n",
      "   \"id\": \"d63df783\",\n",
      "   \"metadata\": {},\n",
      "   \"outputs\": [\n",
      "    {\n",
      "     \"name\": \"stdout\",\n",
      "     \"output_type\": \"stream\",\n",
      "     \"text\": [\n",
      "      \"An error occurred.\\n\"\n",
      "     ]\n",
      "    }\n",
      "   ],\n",
      "   \"source\": [\n",
      "    \"try:\\n\",\n",
      "    \"    num = 0\\n\",\n",
      "    \"    print(10 / num)\\n\",\n",
      "    \"except:\\n\",\n",
      "    \"    print(\\\"An error occurred.\\\")\"\n",
      "   ]\n",
      "  },\n",
      "  {\n",
      "   \"cell_type\": \"code\",\n",
      "   \"execution_count\": 3,\n",
      "   \"id\": \"f827f444\",\n",
      "   \"metadata\": {},\n",
      "   \"outputs\": [\n",
      "    {\n",
      "     \"name\": \"stdout\",\n",
      "     \"output_type\": \"stream\",\n",
      "     \"text\": [\n",
      "      \"File not found.\\n\",\n",
      "      \"Program finished.\\n\"\n",
      "     ]\n",
      "    }\n",
      "   ],\n",
      "   \"source\": [\n",
      "    \"try:\\n\",\n",
      "    \"    file = open(\\\"data.txt\\\", \\\"r\\\")\\n\",\n",
      "    \"    print(file.read())\\n\",\n",
      "    \"\\n\",\n",
      "    \"except FileNotFoundError:\\n\",\n",
      "    \"    print(\\\"File not found.\\\")\\n\",\n",
      "    \"\\n\",\n",
      "    \"finally:\\n\",\n",
      "    \"    print(\\\"Program finished.\\\")\"\n",
      "   ]\n",
      "  }\n",
      " ],\n",
